{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.680", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.960", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verehrte Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.400", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich freue mich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.600", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir uns in diesem Haus \u00fcber alle Fraktionen hinweg einig sind\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.240", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist auch nicht immer der Fall\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.800", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir handeln m\u00fcssen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.560", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dass die Zahl der F\u00e4lle an unseren Verwaltungsgerichten steigt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.520", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das war eigentlich vorhersehbar. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.680", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer ein bisschen Erfahrung hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.040", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die bis in die 80er- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.720", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und bis in die 90er-Jahre reicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.720", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der konnte wissen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.880", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Zahl der F\u00e4lle steigen wird."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.760", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir k\u00f6nnen auch davon ausgehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.880", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die F\u00e4lle nicht ganz unkompliziert werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.680", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gerade angesichts der gro\u00dfen Zahl der schnellen Verfahren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.440", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die das BAMF abwickeln musste. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.280", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da wird auf unsere Verwaltungsgerichte viel zukommen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.800", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich glaube, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.600", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir sind uns darin einig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.440", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir etwas tun m\u00fcssen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.600", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie der Gesetzentwurf von B\u00fcndnis\u00a090/Die Gr\u00fcnen da helfen soll, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.240", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hat sich mir in den letzten Minuten nicht erschlossen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.080", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weder bei der Rede der Kollegin Keul noch bei der Rede des Kollegen Thomae. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.440", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die M\u00f6glichkeit der Berufung einer weiteren Tatsacheninstanz soll erweitert werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.600", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es wurde gerade vom Kollegen Lindh gesagt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.640", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Grund sei, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.080", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Spruchk\u00f6rper zu unterschiedlichen Ergebnissen kommen.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.440", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.160", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es ist nun mal bei Einzelfall\u00adentscheidungen so, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.480", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass man zu unterschiedlichen Ergebnissen kommt; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.080", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn jeder Fall ist anders. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.120", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dahinter verbergen sich ein ganz individueller Werdegang und ein ganz individueller Antrag."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.640", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Frau Kollegin Keul hat gesagt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.560", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Oben kommt nichts an. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.960", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es kommt zu einer unterschiedlichen Rechtsprechung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.760", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das f\u00fchrt zu Unsicherheit.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.760", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jetzt m\u00f6chte ich doch einmal ins Gesetz gucken. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.520", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich habe es mir extra mitgenommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.240", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das schadet ja auch nicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.160", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein Blick ins Gesetz erleichtert die Rechtsfindung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.240", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das lernt man im Studium."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.720", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00a7\u00a078 des Asylgesetzes:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.280", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Urteil des Verwaltungsgerichts, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.840", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "durch das die Klage in Rechtsstreitigkeiten nach diesem Gesetz als offensichtlich unzul\u00e4ssig oder offensichtlich unbegr\u00fcndet abgewiesen wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.400", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist unanfechtbar."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.640", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Absatz\u00a02 steht dann:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.640", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In den \u00fcbrigen F\u00e4llen steht den Beteiligten die Berufung gegen das Urteil des Verwaltungsgerichts zu, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.320", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn sie von dem Oberverwaltungsgericht zugelassen wird."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "137.560", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Berufung ist also m\u00f6glich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "137.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "140.560", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn sie vom Oberverwaltungsgericht zugelassen wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "140.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.320", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich habe mich einmal bei Verwaltungsrichtern umgeh\u00f6rt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.240", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob sie meinen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.360", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "oben bei ihnen komme nichts an. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.320", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.960", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn etwas ankommen soll, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.680", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann geht es auch bei Entscheidungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.280", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die eben nicht offensichtlich unbegr\u00fcndet sind."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.480", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.880", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass bei denen noch eine weitere Tatsacheninstanz m\u00f6glich ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.120", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn man sich ein bisschen mit den Asylverfahren beim BAMF befasst hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.640", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann wei\u00df man, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.040", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sich im Laufe der Zeit Sachverhalte ganz anders darstellen k\u00f6nnen und dass sich der Vortrag der Antragsteller sehr stark ver\u00e4ndern kann."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.880", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie wollen jetzt die M\u00f6glichkeiten der Berufung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.000", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die schon im Gesetz enthalten sind\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.600", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege Thomae hat auf die Sprungrevision hingewiesen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.680", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bei der die rechtlichen Fragen im Streitfall noch gekl\u00e4rt werden k\u00f6nnen\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.280", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "verbreitern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.160", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich m\u00f6chte noch einmal darauf hinweisen und w\u00fcnsche mir, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.040", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass bitte noch einmal alle einen Blick ins Gesetz werfen und feststellen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.040", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es die Berufung schon gibt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.280", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da schafft eine Erweiterung bei der Vielzahl der F\u00e4lle keine Beschleunigung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.000", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie f\u00fchrt vielmehr zur L\u00e4hmung und Verlangsamung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.600", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich empfehle Ihnen einen Blick in die 6.\u00a0VwGO-Novelle aus dem Jahr\u00a01997."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.280", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man muss nicht alles teilen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.680", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was da steht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.280", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber man erkennt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.600", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie bei der gro\u00dfen Klagewelle an den Verwaltungsgerichten einen Erfolg gebracht hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.720", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir hatten in den Jahren fast 500\u00a0000\u00a0Streitigkeiten bei den Verwaltungsgerichten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.760", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Durch sie wurde die Klagewelle einged\u00e4mmt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.200", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sodass unsere Verwaltungsgerichtsbarkeit mit den vielen F\u00e4llen klarkam."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "234.600", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie wollen das jetzt v\u00f6llig negieren und weitere Berufungsm\u00f6glichkeiten schaffen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "234.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.160", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das kann ich verstehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.560", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber nennen Sie es dann nicht Beschleunigung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.480", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dann sollten Sie auch sagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.040", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sie die Berufungsm\u00f6glichkeiten stark erweitern und unsere Justiz bzw. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.320", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unsere Verwaltungsgerichtsbarkeit mit viel, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.360", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "viel mehr F\u00e4llen betrauen wollen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.640", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.640", 
